sequenceDiagram
    participant PF as Promptfoo runner
    participant AP as advisorProvider
    participant CV as Convex action<br/>ai/evals/runOnce
    participant AG as advisor agent
    participant CAT as Convex catalog
    participant SC as scorers
    participant JG as judge model<br/>(Haiku 4.5)

    PF->>AP: callApi(row vars, provider config)
    AP->>CV: action({ question, productId, config })
    CV->>CAT: snapshot(price, rating per productId)
    CV->>AG: invoke with config + context
    AG->>CAT: tool calls (getProductDetails, ...)
    CAT-->>AG: results
    AG-->>CV: parts, tokenUsage, timings, finishReason
    CV-->>AP: { output, tokenUsage, metadata }
    AP-->>PF: result blob

    PF->>SC: programmatic + tool-call-f1
    SC-->>PF: per-assertion scores
    PF->>JG: model-graded rubrics<br/>(question, output)
    JG-->>PF: rubric scores
    PF->>PF: write row × provider cell to JSON
